data.name: CreateDashboardStagingPriority35
ReadCashReceiptDetail1
data.value: select CRV_IDENTIFIER, CST_IDENTIFIER, CRT_IDENTIFIER, CRD_ID, COURT_ORDER_NUMBER, CASE_NUMBER, COLLECTION_AMOUNT, COLLECTION_DATE, OBLGOR_PRSN_NBR, CREATED_TMST, CLT_IDENTIFIER from CKT_CR_DETAIL where (COLLECTION_DATE between cast(@date1 as date) and cast(@date2 as date)) and CLT_IDENTIFIER = 6 and CREATED_TMST < @createdTmst order by CREATED_TMST desc

data.name: ReadCashReceiptDetail2
data.value: select CRV_IDENTIFIER, CST_IDENTIFIER, CRT_IDENTIFIER, CRD_ID, COURT_ORDER_NUMBER, CASE_NUMBER, COLLECTION_AMOUNT, COLLECTION_DATE, OBLGOR_PRSN_NBR, CREATED_TMST, CLT_IDENTIFIER from CKT_CR_DETAIL where OBLGOR_PRSN_NBR = @oblgorPrsnNbr and COURT_ORDER_NUMBER = @courtOrderNumber and CLT_IDENTIFIER = 6 and COLLECTION_DATE = @collectionDate order by CREATED_TMST desc

data.name: ReadCashReceiptDetail3
data.value: select CRV_IDENTIFIER, CST_IDENTIFIER, CRT_IDENTIFIER, CRD_ID, COURT_ORDER_NUMBER, CASE_NUMBER, COLLECTION_AMOUNT, COLLECTION_DATE, OBLGOR_PRSN_NBR, CREATED_TMST, CLT_IDENTIFIER from CKT_CR_DETAIL where OBLGOR_PRSN_NBR = @oblgorPrsnNbr and COURT_ORDER_NUMBER = @courtOrderNumber and CLT_IDENTIFIER = 6 and COLLECTION_DATE < @collectionDate1 and ( COLLECTION_DATE >= @collectionDate2 or COLLECTION_DATE > cast(@createdTstamp as date) )

data.name: ReadDashboardStagingPriority1
data.value: select REPORT_MONTH, REPORT_LEVEL, REPORT_LEVEL_ID, AS_OF_DATE, IWO_PMT_DAYS_NMR, IWO_PMT_DAYS_DNOM, IWO_PMT_DAYS_AVG from CKT_DB_STAGE_PRI35 with(xlock) where REPORT_MONTH = @reportMonth and (REPORT_LEVEL in ('AT', 'CA'))

data.name: ReadDashboardStagingPriority2
data.value: select REPORT_MONTH, REPORT_LEVEL, REPORT_LEVEL_ID, AS_OF_DATE, IWO_PMT_DAYS_NMR, IWO_PMT_DAYS_DNOM, IWO_PMT_DAYS_AVG from CKT_DB_STAGE_PRI35 with(xlock) where REPORT_MONTH = @reportMonth and REPORT_LEVEL = @reportLevel and REPORT_LEVEL_ID = @reportLevelId

data.name: ReadFipsTribunal
data.value: select T1.[STATE], T1.COUNTY, T1.LOCATION, T1.COUNTY_DESC, T1.STATE_ABBREVIATION, T2.TRIBUNAL_NM, T2.JUDICIAL_DISTRICT, T2.IDENTIFIER from CKT_FIPS T1 join CKT_TRIBUNAL T2 on T2.IDENTIFIER = @identifier and T1.LOCATION = T2.FIP_LOCATION and T1.COUNTY = T2.FIP_COUNTY and T1.[STATE] = T2.FIP_STATE and T1.COUNTY > 0

data.name: ReadLegalAction
data.value: select T1.LEGAL_ACTION_ID, T1.CLASSIFICATION, T1.ACTION_TAKEN, T1.TYPE, T1.FILED_DT, T1.INITIATING_STATE, T1.INITIATING_COUNTY, T1.RESPONDING_STATE, T1.RESPONDING_COUNTY, T1.COURT_CASE_NO, T1.END_DT, T1.STANDARD_NO, T1.CREATED_BY, T1.CREATED_TSTAMP, T1.ESTABLISHMENT_CD, T1.TRB_ID from CKT_LEGAL_ACTION T1 where T1.STANDARD_NO = @standardNo and T1.ACTION_TAKEN = 'ORDIWO2' and T1.CREATED_BY <> 'SWELB579' and exists ( select * from CKT_CASE_ROLE T6 join CKT_LEGAL_ACT_PERS T3 join CKT_LA_PER_LA_CROL T4 on T3.LAD_R_NUMBER is not null and T3.ACCOUNT_TYPE = 'R' and T3.LA_PERSON_ID = T4.LAP_ID on T6.CASE_ROLE_ID = T4.CRO_ID and T6.TYPE = T4.CRO_TYPE and T6.CSP_NUMBER = T4.CSP_NUM and T6.CAS_NUMBER = T4.CAS_NUM and T6.TYPE = 'AP' and T6.END_DATE >= @endDate and T6.CSP_NUMBER = @cspNumber where T1.LEGAL_ACTION_ID = T3.LGA_R_IDENTIFIER ) order by T1.CREATED_TSTAMP desc

data.name: ReadLegalActionAssigmentServiceProvider
data.value: select T1.LGA_IDENTIFIER, T1.OSP_EFFECTIVE_DATE, T1.OSP_ROLE_CODE, T1.OFF_GENERATED_ID, T1.SPD_GENERATED_ID, T1.EFFECTIVE_DT, T1.END_DT, T1.REASON_CODE, T1.CREATED_TIMESTAMP, T2.SERVICE_PRVDER_ID, T2.USER_ID, T2.ROLE_CODE from CKT_SERVICE_PRVDER T2 join CKT_LA_SERV_PROV T1 on @lgaIdentifier = T1.LGA_IDENTIFIER and T1.EFFECTIVE_DT <= cast(@createdTstamp as date) and T1.END_DT >= cast(@createdTstamp as date) and T1.OSP_ROLE_CODE is not null and T1.OSP_EFFECTIVE_DATE is not null and T1.OFF_GENERATED_ID is not null and T2.SERVICE_PRVDER_ID = T1.SPD_GENERATED_ID order by T1.EFFECTIVE_DT desc

data.name: ReadLegalActionIncomeSourceCsePerson
data.value: select T1.CSP_NUMBER, T1.LGA_IDENTIFIER, T1.ISR_IDENTIFIER, T1.EFFECTIVE_DT, T1.CREATED_TSTAMP, T1.WITHHOLDING_TYPE, T1.END_DT, T1.WAGE_OR_NON_WAGE, T1.ORDER_TYPE, T1.IDENTIFIER from CKT_LEGAL_ACT_ISRC T1 where @lgaIdentifier = T1.LGA_IDENTIFIER and exists ( select * from CKT_INCOME_SOURCE T3 where T3.CSP_I_NUMBER = T1.CSP_NUMBER and T3.IDENTIFIER = T1.ISR_IDENTIFIER and T3.EMP_ID is not null and T3.CSP_I_NUMBER = @cspINumber and T3.TYPE = 'E' ) order by T1.END_DT desc

data.name: UpdateDashboardStagingPriority1
data.value: update CKT_DB_STAGE_PRI35 set IWO_PMT_DAYS_NMR = @iwoPmtDaysNmr, IWO_PMT_DAYS_DNOM = @iwoPmtDaysDnom, IWO_PMT_DAYS_AVG = @iwoPmtDaysAvg where REPORT_MONTH = @reportMonth and REPORT_LEVEL = @reportLevel and REPORT_LEVEL_ID = @reportLevelId

data.name: UpdateDashboardStagingPriority2
data.value: update CKT_DB_STAGE_PRI35 set AS_OF_DATE = @asOfDate, IWO_PMT_DAYS_NMR = @iwoPmtDaysNmr, IWO_PMT_DAYS_DNOM = @iwoPmtDaysDnom, IWO_PMT_DAYS_AVG = @iwoPmtDaysAvg where REPORT_MONTH = @reportMonth and REPORT_LEVEL = @reportLevel and REPORT_LEVEL_ID = @reportLevelId
